-- Chongqing Machinery to Discuss Acquisition of Hyva, Financial Times Says
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   R i c h a r d s
-- 2010-11-09T22:16:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/chongqing-machinery-to-discuss-acquisition-of-hyva-financial-times-says.html
Chongqing Machinery and Electric Co
Ltd. will this week hold talks with 3i Group Plc about the
potential acquisition of Hyva for 600 million euros, the
Financial Times reported, without saying where it got the
information from. Hyva is based in the Netherlands, according to
the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Richards at 
 vrichards@bloomberg.net  